T02D2332:276a-29: bla ma dam pa'i gdams ngag la //
T02D2332:276a-30: chu bo'i rgyun bzhin nyams blangs na //
T02D2332:276a-31: dam tshig de yis skong bar gsungs //
T02D2332:276a-32: rmi lam mngon sum gang la yang //
T02D2332:276a-33: cho 'phrul sna tshogs byung ba la //
T02D2332:276a-34: sgyu mar shes na lam du 'gyur //
T02D2332:276a-35: bden par bzung na bar chod yin //
T02D2332:276a-36: dngos grub rnam gnyis thob pa na //
T02D2332:276a-37: bar chad lam gyi grogs su 'char //
T02D2332:276a-38: gsang sngags thabs kyi lam mchog gi //
T02D2332:276a-39: mkha' 'gro gsang ba'i bcud bsdus pa //
T02D2332:276a-40: snying po 'di ni bla na med //
T02D2332:276a-41: skal ldan rnams kyi spyod yul lo //
T02D2332:276a-42: 'di ni thabs lam bka' dpe kun la ma gnang ba yin no //
